high_descs: Turn right and reach the desk on the right side
Take the butter knife from the desk
Hold the butter knife and move towards the cup
Put the butter knife in the cup
Take the cup along with butter knife in hand
Little bit move towards the right side to reach the drawer on which oven is placed
Open the drawer and put the cup along with butter knife in it and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: put the cup along with butter knife in the drawer

high_descs: Turn around and go to the desk on your left.
Pick up the butter knife in front of the cup on the desk.
Go to the cup on the table.
Put the butter knife in the cup on the desk.
Pick up the cup with the butter knife on the desk.
Turn right, go straight and turn to the microwave to your left.
Put the cup with the butter knife in the middle drawer under the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To put a cup with a butter knife inside a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the desk
Pick up butter knife from the desk
Move towards the cup
Put Butter knife into the cup
Pick butter knife along with cup
Turn around and walk to the drawer to your left
Place cup inside the drawer and close it
anns.task_desc: Shifting butter knife and cup from one place to another
